Package ui

Class Gui

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
ui.MainLayout
ui.Gui
public class Gui extends MainLayout
The Gui class represents the graphical user interface for the eshop. It extends MainLayout and initializes the main stages and scenes for the application.

The class sets up the login and registration scenes using the Authentication class and applies the specified CSS styles. It also configures the main layout and scene for the application.
